---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="About — 8EyeTieDye"
  description="The story behind 8EyeTieDye — AI-generated tie-dye merch that's truly one of a kind."
>
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-3xl">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold dye-gradient-text mb-8"
    >
      About 8EyeTieDye
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg space-y-6 text-gray-300">
      <p>
        8EyeTieDye was born from a simple idea: what if every piece of clothing
        was truly one-of-a-kind?
      </p>

      <p>
        Traditional tie-dye is beautiful but unpredictable. We took that
        creative chaos and combined it with AI to create something new — designs
        that are generated in real-time, never repeated, and printed on premium
        apparel just for you.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        The Spider
      </h2>
      <p>
        Our mascot sees the world through 8 eyes — each one spotting a different
        pattern, a different possibility. Like a spider spinning its web, every
        design we create is intricate, unique, and spun just for you.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        How We Make It
      </h2>
      <p>
        We use state-of-the-art AI image generation (FLUX.2) to create tie-dye
        patterns that range from classic spirals to psychedelic masterpieces.
        Each design is generated at high resolution, then printed using
        sublimation printing for vibrant, all-over coverage that won't crack,
        peel, or fade.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        True Scarcity
      </h2>
      <p>
        Every design exists exactly once. If you don't purchase within 24 hours,
        it disappears forever. No reprints, no restocks, no duplicates. What you
        spin is yours alone.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-12">
        All designs are AI-generated using the FLUX.2 model. 8EyeTieDye is a
        Kinchito Commerce brand.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
